{"tid":1772811,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"叱吒903：每週冠軍歌合集2019 (Spotify, KKBOX, MOOV, YouTube) - 娛樂台","createTime":"2019-12-07T03:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T07:19:29.000Z","uid":184592,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90b8ee50a02715c7ce370c60cc5fdb00b660ce97","tid":1772811,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每週冠軍歌</span></span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>Spotify - </strong></span><a href=\"https://spoti.fi/2DQxZFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspoti.fi%2F2DQxZFs&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=bcdd708d\" target=\"_blank\">https://spoti.fi/2DQxZFs</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>KKBOX - </strong></span><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Yvvwd5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Yvvwd5&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=acdaf48e\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Yvvwd5</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>MOOV - </strong></span><a href=\"http://bit.ly/34Yc2jN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34Yc2jN&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=1fe09908\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/34Yc2jN</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YouTube - </strong></span><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Lv345W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Lv345W&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=ed38fe87\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Lv345W</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不過認真講<br />\n上得冠軍歌嘅8成都係中至慢版Cantopop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n聽3至5首你仲頂得順，咁聽10首、20首呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有商業利益交換，又可以買位<br />\n所以上得冠軍歌，或者上得叱吒頒獎台嘅，我敢講未必係年度最出色嘅出品<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有咩出色作品我唔講了，廢事俾人話打手，不如自己聽啦</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面嘅<strong>「無限LOOP playlist」</strong><br />\n有晒近期903上榜又好聽嘅本地快歌、另類、Pop Rock、Jazz Pop、Cantopop, etc.<br />\n樓主我將類近mood同節拍嘅歌砌埋一齊，希望大家聽得順耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>Spotify - </strong></span><a href=\"https://spoti.fi/38dUger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspoti.fi%2F38dUger&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=672f3062\" target=\"_blank\">https://spoti.fi/38dUger</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>KKBOX - </strong></span><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OYhZHS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OYhZHS&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=c5b64b8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OYhZHS</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>MOOV - </strong></span><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Ukypyx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ukypyx&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=40bfa6de\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Ukypyx</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YouTube - </strong></span><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2UjUywW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UjUywW&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=c6405390\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2UjUywW</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我仲砌咗其他Playlist，有興趣就睇以下post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/982281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/982281</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>利伸，唔係903打手，點解跟903？</strong><br />\n因為新歌太多，私人時間太少，我自己聽唔晒咁多歌，唯有跟903網頁update自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5115f